at_Bustard",["Animal","Asia","Binomial_nomenclature","Bird","Bird_migration","British_Isles","Carolus_Linnaeus","Chordate","Europe","Hungary","Scientific_classification"]),("Great_Comet_of_1882",["Aristotle","Cape_Town","Comet","Great_comet","South_Africa","Sun"]),("Great_Crested_Grebe",["Africa","Animal","Asia","Binomial_nomenclature","Bird","Bird_migration","Carolus_Linnaeus","Chordate","Crustacean","Europe","Extinction","Insect","Scientific_classification","United_Kingdom"]),("Great_Lakes_Storm_of_1913",["Autumn","Canada","Cereal","Chicago","Cleveland%2C_Ohio","Coal","Great_Lakes","Gulf_of_Mexico","Lake_Superior","Meteorology","Mississippi_River","Natural_disaster","North_America","Rain","Rocky_Mountains","Ship","Snow","Telephone","Tropical_cyclone","United_States","United_States_dollar","Washington%2C_D.C.","Weather_forecasting"]),("Weather_forecasting",["20th_century","Aristotle","Climate_change","Computer","Earth%27s_atmosphere","Europe","Meteorology","Physics","Snow","Weather"]),("Slavic_mythology",["Australia","Black_Sea","God","Halloween","Melbourne","Mythology","Prague","Religion","Trinity"]),("Sea_of_Galilee",["Arabic_language","Banana","Byzantine_Empire","Crusades","Dead_Sea","Earthquake","Egypt","France","Great_Rift_Valley","Hebrew_language","Israel","Jerusalem","Jesus","Jordan","Jordan_River","Roman_Empire","Saladin","Sea","Sermon_on_the_Mount","Syria","United_Kingdom","Volcano","West_Bank","Zionism"]),("Great_Spotted_Woodpecker",["Animal","Asia","Beetle","Binomial_nomenclature","Bird","Carolus_Linnaeus","Chordate","Europe","Insect","Scientific_classification","Woodpecker"]),("Great_hammerhead",["Animal","Binomial_nomenclature","Chordate","Scientific_classification"]),("Greater_Cane_Rat",["Africa","Animal","Binomial_nomenclature","Ghana","Mammal","Scientific_classification"]),("Tenzin_Gyatso%2C_14th_Dalai_Lama",["Archbishop_of_Canterbury","Barley","Beijing","Canada","Canadian_House_of_Commons","China","Culture","Democracy","Desmond_Tutu","Eastern_Ortho
